intent.user_query: How does the average order value change over different seasons (assuming seasons based on month)?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT CASE WHEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM SaleDate) IN (12, 1, 2) THEN 'Winter' WHEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM SaleDate) IN (3, 4, 5) THEN 'Spring' WHEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM SaleDate) IN (6, 7, 8) THEN 'Summer' ELSE 'Fall' END AS Season, AVG(TotalAmount) AS AverageOrderValue FROM fitness_db.Sales GROUP BY 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT CASE WHEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM SaleDate) IN (12, 1, 2) THEN 'Winter' WHEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM SaleDate) IN (3, 4, 5) THEN 'Spring' WHEN EXTRACT(MONTH FROM SaleDate) IN (6, 7, 8) THEN 'Summer' ELSE 'Fall' END AS Season, AVG(TotalAmount) AS AverageOrderValue FROM fitness_db.Sales GROUP BY 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
